    "\n",
    "> **Colab option:** run cells 0–5 locally to clear the gate, then run the dense embed on a Colab GPU and copy the cache `.npy`/`.meta.json` back into `data/embeddings_n300/`. Or just run the whole notebook wherever the embed runs."
